What a year(s)! We're proud to present you with what we consider to be the best of every indie release released within the last two years.
This edition includes some new tracks, new versions, and updates to audio quality for many songs that were originally unavailable in high quality. Enjoy!
(a list of the changed/added/fixed tracks will be provided in thegroup upon request)


Special thanks to Jonathan F. for piecing together the intro from various used and unused band recordings we've recieved.


Thanks to the bands that submitted their music in high quality.


Thanks to the IRPgroup for sharing their favorite tracks each month. They were catalogued and used as a guideline for songs that should be included for this bi-yearly playlist.
